Spring Boot 101: Part7 - Configuration

1. application.propergies file
 1.1 Change to Spring Boot Server port
   - server.port=8082
 
 1.2 Add app-mode in the application.propergies file
   - app-mode=development
 
 1.3 Modify ViewController.java
   - Implement Dependency Injection based on Property or 
   - Implement Dependency Injection based on Constructor and Add @Autowired annotation 
     (We don't need to change another source code just it needs to change application.properties file)